Interface URIResponse

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    FetchData, HttpResponseWarcRecord

    public interface URIResponse
    An interface implemented by all classes able to expose a HttpResponse and URI, e.g. HttpResponseWarcRecord or FetchData.
